Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神經系統以及視覺信息的處理 果然發現異常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一時的修復挺順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但推測最多能堅持10小時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.13,0:02:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2500年前的DNA真是麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我徹底的修改與神經開路形成有關的遺傳程序
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天之前給我解決
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...我想出去外面一會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒完成 請服從我的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你繼續檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們監視HRF12
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:02:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能大意了 20年前也有實驗體逃跑的先例
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿 鹿 鹿...煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼結緣...邂逅 根本就沒有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這你就不懂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛啊 當你遇到了就會覺得無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心一意的愛戀...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心一意的愛戀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...什...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個毛色古怪的鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的書包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 還不還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等...等...哇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是廢物 你們幹嘛去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何要給我把她抓回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長 她是從這裡逃跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HRF12 不要做蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來去哪 去不去東大寺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想看大佛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聲音太大啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想把書包拿到哪裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都差點被你害死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇得我半死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還搞我迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再纏著我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:05:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柿本真一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是倭跡跡日百襲姫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倭...跡跡...跡跡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我跡跡就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跡跡 你是這附近的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈良 真是個好玩的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是佛像啊 古墳什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 像這樣子逛街我還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 真一你見過大海嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海？ 肯定見過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羨慕啊 大海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒見過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為哪裡都不讓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 問你一些奇怪的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也有走失過 哪裡也去不了...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去逛逛嗎 奈良的大街小巷
