Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一 真是惟妙惟肖的...佛像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興福寺 阿修羅立像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中宮寺 彌勒菩薩半跏思惟像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐招提寺 千手觀音菩薩立像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了 要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一 真一 真一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一 真一 真一...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,400)\fs45\1c&H0000ff}緊急呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現HRF12
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她正和疑是犯人的男性 以及之前的那隻鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向這邊逃竄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了 我們過去接人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子是不是太不禮貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好雄偉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 據說如果穿過了大佛的鼻孔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四天後 願望就能成真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻孔？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移動 請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移動 請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移動 請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說現在...移動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.45,0:09:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佛的鼻孔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊 這樣的話應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.54,0:09:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要被吸進去一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒...沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 完全沒問...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吸進去了 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你嚇壞我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂...喂...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會 機會 夢寐以求的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胡說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我想從健康的邂逅開始...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是穿過了大佛的鼻子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是大佛賜予你的大好良機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我沒那種打算
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跡跡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 我必須回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你陪我玩了一天 真的好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次 一起去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一 趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HRF12 快下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HRF12？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.27,0:11:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想動粗 乖乖聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面那個男的 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跡跡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 和他沒有關係 請放他走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了 要是抵抗的話就給她點苦頭吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了麼 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一 抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:11:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HRF12 造反了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛陀大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一 真一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔社長 媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來拖延時間 你快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跡跡你也一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了 我不想把你牽扯進來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跡跡 跡跡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跡跡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跡跡 跡跡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:13:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去找
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢夥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢把媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那狼狽的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右制衡神經和左電荷神經發現異常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快聯絡機構
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我為了你賭上了多少年的青春嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的整個人生 全賭上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為是誰把你這嘴硬的傢夥製造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這鼻子 這眼睛 這張臉 這具身體 都是誰製造的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣 我也會哭 會笑 會怒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會愛上一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 必須獨活於世的你 竟會說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一小時 你就會變成一堆廢品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把她搬走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跡跡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:16:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跡跡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.41,0:17:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跡跡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是你 還是實驗體 還有你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去海邊吧 現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一 奈良是沒有海的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不試試
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:17:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼 鹿？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跡跡 那個...我...跡...跡你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜...喜...
