Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.42,0:22:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想幹什麼 你們
